{"tid":1677380,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(正視聽)咁多國家逆權抗暴，香港係最地獄mode嗰個","createTime":"2019-10-27T05:20:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-27T10:44:00.000Z","uid":74155,"like":87,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"29a1594ec14d963e8b04aebc1d7a10bd112b109e","tid":1677380,"uid":74155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T05:20:46.000Z","msg":"點解？<br />\n歐洲(氣候)、加泰、俄羅斯<br />\n印尼、韓國<br />\n黎巴嫩、伊拉克<br />\n智利、海地<br />\n佢哋全部都係民選政府，政府係會諗選票，驚民意，甚至連軍隊都可以唔聽政府支笛因為人哋軍隊屬於國家亦即人民㗎<br />\n<br />\n而唯獨係得香港<br />\n政府係殖民傀儡政權，係軍政府<br />\n完全唔使理民意逆天而行<br />\n因為佢哋效忠中國國家社會主義(即中國納粹主義)政權，<br />\n最首要目標係清洗、滅絕成個香港族群<br />\n所以，<br />\n我哋嘅抗爭係無可能幾個月就完到<br />\n唔同人哋其他國家個政府會一陣即跪<br />\n所以各位手足要認清事實，<br />\n調整好心態<br />\n我哋係打緊反法西斯主義戰爭<br />\n人哋真係純粹示威㗎咋，<br />\n人哋有退路，我哋一退就跌落懸崖"},{"pid":"db7de46da5636165b5cba17d6885fa1971e76601","tid":1677380,"uid":74155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T05:25:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f18e2342fddc781167fdbb0345831a4e4de041b3","tid":1677380,"uid":169079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T05:25:52.000Z","msg":"我哋係最難，但係有強力大佬美國撐緊，正面啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3171581b39297e845a847cd266f93f097cd18359","tid":1677380,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T05:26:02.000Z","msg":"可唔可以唔好剩係懲罰出名嘅黃店？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1675556\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1675556</a>"},{"pid":"525ea4d843c1abfb942c1b69d5725fc973969cc8","tid":1677380,"uid":134774,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T05:27:12.000Z","msg":"中國係nazi level<br />\n其他mini boss<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67475d282ef0c946d551cdd9c31b7fcb6d561217","tid":1677380,"uid":73565,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T05:29:11.000Z","msg":"人地係示威<br />\n香港